data.description: This beautifully maintained single family home sits in the heart of Schenectady's Bellevue section. Featuring 3 bedrooms, 1 full bathroom, living room, formal dining room, kitchen, a great room and second dining room. This home has heating and cooling central air systems that was installed less than 8 years ago. This property is close proximity to Van Corlaer Elementary School, shopping and local restaurants. This home is waiting for its new owner to call it home. Don't miss out on the opportunity. Call to schedule your private tour today!
